		<h4>I just sent a referral to my friend - now what?</h4>
		<p>If your friend makes their first deal purchase within 72 hours from the time they click on the referral link you send them, you'll see that we've put $10 credit in your account.</p>

		<h4>Can I refer as many people as I want?</h4>
		<p><a href="<%= refer_a_friend_publisher_consumers_path(@publisher) %>">Yes!</a></p>

		<h4>I received referral links from three people - do they all get rewarded?</h4>
		<p>No, only the last link you click on before making your first purchase will generate a reward for the person who sent it to you. </p>

